---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | idktheflag">
    <main class="container">
        <h1>About idktheflag</h1>
        
        <div class="terminal-box">
            <p><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami</p>
            <p><strong>[STATUS]:</strong> Active (very)</p>
            <p><strong>[SPECIALTY]:</strong> depends on who on the team ur referring to</p>
            <p><strong>[MOTTO]:</strong> "i forgor what the flag is"</p>
        </div>

        <section class="prose">
            <p>
			We are <strong>idktheflag</strong>, a Capture The Flag (CTF) team born out of <s>late-night debugging sessions, excessive caffeine consumption, and a shared hatred for light mode.</s> our shared singular brain cell.
            </p>
            <p>
			Our logo is drawn in MS Paint, but our exploits are written in <s>Python, C</s> and sheer willpower. We compete in global CTF tournaments, breaking <s>cryptography, grooming heaps, and popping shells</s> our fucking sanity.
            </p>
            
            <h2>The Roster</h2>
            <ul class="roster-list">
				<li><strong>(C)<i>riverxia</i></strong> — legit everything lol (carry w)</li>
				<li><strong>(C)<i>qu1ck5h0t</i></strong> — cryptography</li>
				<li><em>zemi/immattas</em> — pwn</li>
				<li><em>nila</em> — forensics/web/a bit of everything</li>
				<li><em>cloud</em> - coach + gen player</li>
            </ul>
			<h2>Retired/Semi-Active</h2>
            <ul class="roster-list">
				<li><em>Aw</em> — general</li>
				<li><em>skillz</em> — epic coach</li>
				<li><em>noatwill1024</em> — chad</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Join the Chaos</h2>
            <p>
                Check out our <a href="/blog">write-ups</a> to see how poorly we tackle challenges, or hit up our <a href="https://github.com/idktheflag" target="_blank">GitHub</a> to see how dum we are
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .terminal-box {
        background-color: #161b22;
        border: 1px solid #30363d;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .terminal-box p {
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        color: #e6edf3;
    }

    .prompt {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .prose h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: var(--text-heading);
    }

    .roster-list {
        list-style-type: square;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .roster-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }
</style>
